rows.label: bf08010100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ](waking moan)

rows.label: bf08010100_0020
rows.name: Hikari...

rows.label: bf08010100_0030
rows.name: Rex...?

rows.label: bf08010100_0040
rows.name: All in one piece?

rows.label: bf08010100_0050
rows.name: I guess if you were injured, I'd be feeling it too...

rows.label: bf08010100_0060
rows.name:
Huh?
Yes, I'm OK.

rows.label: bf08010100_0070
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!

rows.label: bf08010100_0080
rows.name:
W-was I...
...in your lap...

rows.label: bf08010100_0082
rows.name: this whole time?

rows.label: bf08010100_0090
rows.name: Mm. It's like the opposite of when we met.

rows.label: bf08010100_0100
rows.name:
...By the way, I see you're back
to your old self.

rows.label: bf08010100_0105
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]ADLIB

rows.label: bf08010100_0110
rows.name: I mean...th-thank you...

rows.label: bf08010100_0120
rows.name: I...didn't say anything strange, did I?

rows.label: bf08010100_0130
rows.name:
Talking in my sleep, or grinding my teeth, or snoring, or...
I'm such a terrible sleeper...

rows.label: bf08010100_0140
rows.name: You snore and grind your teeth?

rows.label: bf08010100_0150
rows.name:
O-Of course I don't,
I-It was just a figure of speech, how rude.

rows.label: bf08010100_0160
rows.name:
Hahaha!
It's OK.

rows.label: bf08010100_0170
rows.name:
What with all the fighting and stuff...
You were out for the count.

rows.label: bf08010100_0180
rows.name: R-right... That's good to know...

rows.label: bf08010100_0190
rows.name:
Where are we...?
Where is everyone...?

rows.label: bf08010100_0200
rows.name: We're under the Cloud Sea...

rows.label: bf08010100_0210
rows.name:
This must be the place us salvagers call...
the Land of Mors.

rows.label: bf08010100_0220
rows.name:
I don't know what happened to everyone else...
Over there is where we fell.

rows.label: bf08010100_0230
rows.name: From all the way up there...

rows.label: bf08010100_0240
rows.name:
Looks like there's some kinda powerful
updraft coming from below...

rows.label: bf08010100_0250
rows.name:
It saved us.
I wonder if it caught the others too.

rows.label: bf08010100_0260
rows.name: I'm sure it did.

rows.label: bf08010100_0270
rows.name: Yeah...

rows.label: bf08010100_0280
rows.name:
Still OK?
Let's get our bearings and then go look for them.

rows.label: bf08010100_0290
rows.name: We need to find a way out of here...

rows.label: bf08010100_0300
rows.name: Any ideas?

rows.label: bf08010100_0310
rows.name: Over there.

rows.label: bf08010100_0320
rows.name: Are those...the World Tree's roots?

rows.label: bf08010100_0330
rows.name:
Yeah...
I bet there's a way up there.

rows.label: bf08010100_0340
rows.name:
There has to be.
I'm good to go. Let's move!

rows.label: bf08010100_0350
rows.name: Uh, how's Homura?

rows.label: bf08010100_0360
rows.name: She's sleeping. Shall I call her?

rows.label: bf08010100_0370
rows.name:
Nah, let her sleep.
She's been through a lot.

rows.label: bf08010100_0380
rows.name: You're too kind.

rows.label: bf08010100_0390
rows.name: Rule five of the Salvager Code!

rows.label: bf08010100_0400
rows.name: Men should al-

rows.label: bf08010100_0410
rows.name: I don't think we need to hear it.

rows.label: bf08010100_0412
rows.name: C'mon! Let's go!

rows.label: bf08010100_0420
rows.name:
Heeey!
At least let me finish, spoilsport.
